sequenceDiagram
  actor Student
  participant Web as React Web Client
  participant API as TutorController
  participant Auth as AuthGuard
  participant Tutor as TutorService
  participant Profile as StudentProfileService
  participant Background as BackgroundAiService
  participant Knowledge as KnowledgeService
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant AIModel as AiModelService
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI-backed model provider

  Student->>Web: Type prompt or use speech recognition
  Web->>API: POST /tutor/message
  API->>Auth: Validate session cookie
  Auth-->>API: Authenticated user
  API->>Tutor: answerMessage(user, message, source)
  Tutor->>Profile: getTutorContext(userId)
  Profile->>DB: Read student_profiles
  DB-->>Profile: Profile summary and strategy
  Profile-->>Tutor: Tutor profile context
  Tutor->>Knowledge: getActiveVectorStoreIds()
  Knowledge->>DB: Read knowledge_files when env ids absent
  Knowledge-->>Tutor: Vector store ids
  Tutor->>AIModel: Create response with profile context and optional file_search
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Structured tutor JSON and citations
  AIModel-->>Tutor: Provider response
  Tutor->>DB: Insert tutor_turn
  Tutor->>Background: enqueueTutorTurnWork()
  alt Background batching enabled
    Background->>DB: Insert background_learning_observations
    Background->>DB: Schedule or reschedule learning_window_analysis job
  else Legacy background mode
    Background->>DB: Insert per-turn background_ai_jobs
  end
  Tutor-->>API: TutorAnswer
  API-->>Web: Answer, tasks, examples, citations, image prompt
  Note over Background,AIModel: Later drain groups stored observations by window size, idle timeout, or quality trigger
  Background->>DB: Read pending observations and job queue
  Background->>AIModel: Window analysis with optional flex tier and prompt cache key
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Learning-window JSON
  AIModel-->>Background: Parsed model response
  Background->>DB: Store analysis window and student_learning_signals
  opt Profile refresh interval reached
    Background->>AIModel: Combined profile/strategy refresh
    AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
    OpenAI-->>AIModel: Profile and strategy patch JSON
    AIModel-->>Background: Parsed model response
    Background->>DB: Update student_profiles
  end
  opt Image needed
    Student->>Web: Request diagram
    Web->>API: POST /tutor/image
    API->>Tutor: generateImage(prompt, context)
    Tutor->>AIModel: Generate explanatory PNG
    AIModel->>OpenAI: Images API request
    OpenAI-->>AIModel: Base64 image
    AIModel-->>Tutor: Image response
    Tutor-->>API: Data URL
    API-->>Web: Render generated image
  end
